ryad.games.ergoengine
Class GameObject

java.lang.Object
  ryad.games.ergoengine.BaseObject
      ryad.games.ergoengine.GameObject
All Implemented Interfaces:
ActionListener
public class GameObject
extends BaseObject

GameObjects are all objects that can be seen, collided with, moved, etc. This basic class does little more than store data in which components use to communicate to each other through.

Author:
Jason Welch
